tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE 3d_printing_failures (
    print_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    failure_reason TEXT,
    failure_date DATE,
    printer_model TEXT,
    filaments_used TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE printing_failures (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  date DATE,
  failure_type VARCHAR,
  failure_description TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE printer_models (
  model_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  model_name VARCHAR,
  manufacturer VARCHAR,
  release_year INT
)

CREATE TABLE print_materials (
  material_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  material_name VARCHAR,
  material_type VARCHAR,
  supplier VARCHAR
)

CREATE TABLE print_jobs (
  job_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  printer_id INT,
  material_id INT,
  start_time TIMESTAMP,
  end_time TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE printers (
  printer_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  printer_name VARCHAR,
  model_id INT,
  purchase_date DATE,
  printer_location VARCHAR
)
